Dialogue: 2,0:16:05.80,0:16:10.66,英,,0,0,0,,On that notes, huge thanks to Olaf Stroosma, René van Paassen, and Max Mulder
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.66,0:16:15.23,中,,0,0,0,,在此 非常感谢代尔夫特大学航空航天工程学院 控制与仿真部的\NOlaf Stroosma、René van Paassen和Max Mulder
